+"----------------------------------------------------------------------------
+"  Description: Vim Ada syntax file
+"     Language: Ada (2005)
+"	   $Id: vim-7.1-ada.patch,v 1.1 2008/01/16 15:58:14 karsten Exp $
+"    Copyright: Copyright (C) 2006 Martin Krischik
+"   Maintainer: Martin Krischik
